entries.text: I gave these to my daughter Alyx for Christmas. There is a limit to the colors you can get in straight PLA so I printed these in White and painted them. The first pair broke as soon as she expanded her headphones. I printed a second pair and increased the overall size by 50%. This made the mounts thicker and stronger. With the larger size I didn't want the fill pattern creeping in the supports so I also increased the wall thickness when generating the G-Code.
entries.name: Painted Ears
